overview.en: ZAYN is a digital cash developed on the basis of block chain technology, with real enterprise products and resources as the value endorsement, real industry marketization as the application scenario, and the profitability of related real enterprises as the expectation.
overview.zh: ZAYN是一个基于区块链技术开发，以实体企业产品及资源作为价值背书，以实体产业市场化作为应用场景，以其所涉及关联的实体企业的盈利能力为预期，所开发的一款数字货币.
